Package: IReports2
Type: Package
Title: INWTlab Templates for Business Reports
Description: This R package provides a LaTeX and RMarkdown template suitable for business
  reports. The design and layout is loosly oriented at MS Word defaults. In the
  YAML header of the RMarkdown template, you can easily customize the colors,
  logos and cover page.
Version: 0.11.0
Author: Sarah Wagner, Karol Kozio≈Ç
Maintainer: Sarah Wagner <sarah.wagner@inwt-statistics.de>
